{"tid":788193,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"MAMAMOO頌樂苦練鋼管舞 性感演出全場尖叫","createTime":"2018-08-21T09:32:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T19:00:10.000Z","uid":51412,"like":17,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0f4844dc470dbc48384f5b49c4bc3d488a496dc6","tid":788193,"uid":51412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T09:32:05.000Z","msg":"MAMAMOO的亞洲巡迴演唱會《2018 MAMAMOO CONCERT 4season S/S》在首爾揭幕，隊長頌<br />\n樂更準備了特別演出，大跳鋼管舞，令全場尖叫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/4IkxUrk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2F4IkxUrk.jpg&h=5669a158&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/UP3nraM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FUP3nraM.jpg&h=0fc84c83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這次亞巡以首爾作起點，一連兩日在首爾奧林匹克公園手球競技場舉行演唱會。早前以性<br />\n感風回歸的MAMAMOO，這次演唱會也加入不少性感元素。頌樂為了重現新歌MV中的鋼管舞<br />\n場面，更積極練習，打算把最好一面獻給粉絲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/hT1bkE4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FhT1bkE4.jpg&h=82c5ed94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/4SVEFUr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2F4SVEFUr.jpg&h=f8b4afd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/4k3xNxH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2F4k3xNxH.jpg&h=82a5e620&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n頌樂在演唱會當天穿著全黑的蕾絲服裝登場，優雅地在鋼管上轉圈，美妙的體態和表現媲<br />\n美專業的鋼管舞者，引來全場尖叫不斷！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/mnGrJjI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FmnGrJjI.jpg&h=944349f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/fYG8siu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FfYG8siu.jpg&h=ea9f0b06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/H0XlSnx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FH0XlSnx.jpg&h=63d4510b&s={SIZE}